257.title: Star Trek
notes:
Comics adaptations of the television and film series, periodicals beginning here with the 1967-1979 Gold Key comic book series. Other series include
  • Marvel Comics series 1980 to 1982
  • DC Comics series 1984 to 1988
  • DC Comics series 1989 to 1996
  • IDW Publishing series 2011 to 2016.

See also the reprint series

  • A Dynabrite Comic
  • Star Trek (IDW trade paperback volumes)
  • Star Trek : Gold Key Archives
  • Star Trek : The Key Collection
  • Star Trek Archives
  • Star Trek Classics
and related series
  • The Original Crew
  • Star Trek Alien Spotlight
  • Star Trek Annual
  • Star Trek Deep Space Nine
  • Star Trek the Next Generation
plus one-off parodies Star Trek--Parodies, Imitations Etc. and parody series (two of them) both called Star Bleech. Adaptations of the first movie are at Star Trek, the Motion Picture. Characters with separate lists in this index include Klingons.
